Given the following array of dictionaries, write a function in Python to find and return the longest common prefix in the keys of dictionaries.arr_of_dictionaries = [
    {
        "name": "John Doe",
        "country": "United States"
    },
    {
        "name": "Jane Doe",
        "state": "New York"
